permafrost.tundra.flow

Class VariableSubstitutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • permafrost.tundra.flow.VariableSubstitutor

  • public class VariableSubstitutor
extends java.lang.Object
    Performs webMethods Integration Server flow language variable substitution on percent-delimited strings.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      VariableSubstitutor(java.lang.String substitutionString, com.wm.data.IData scope)
      Constructs a new VariableSubstitutor object for performing variable substitution on the given string by replacing all occurrences of substrings matching "%key%" with the associated value from a specified scope.
      VariableSubstitutor(java.lang.String substitutionString, java.lang.String defaultValue, com.wm.data.IData scope)
      Constructs a new VariableSubstitutor object for performing variable substitution on the given string by replacing all occurrences of substrings matching "%key%" with the associated value from a specified scope; if the key has no value, the given defaultValue (if not null) is used instead.
